{"tid":2277553,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"結婚拍片劇本","createTime":"2020-11-08T14:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T17:10:30.000Z","uid":1216,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5bbc8dde30d586088688be6deb72a30dc6381d7f","tid":2277553,"uid":1216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"話說小弟過幾日結婚，想註冊當日拍片做個紀念。<br />\n由於只搵左一個朋友幫手影相，打算自己拍片。<br />\n但一直都諗唔到個劇本，想大家幫幫手出謀獻策。<br />\n時間係一個朝早，下午就去會堂註冊。<br />\n無兄弟無姐妹，拍攝器材有2部相機，1部action cam"},{"pid":"7c1ea3083783bcd72b22891afbdc22924f3d8666","tid":2277553,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"比錢請人好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c429cc78a61f92f2598c58d0dcabb5bca9b88cf","tid":2277553,"uid":1216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c1ea3083783bcd72b22891afbdc22924f3d8666","tid":2277553,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"比錢請人好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"有1個朋友幫手影相而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我地只係註冊而已，無個d 傳統禮儀習俗，簡簡單單，所以拍片都係打算自己搞掂"},{"pid":"b9de7fcffcaaf2ebb95f9c5ce832d5ed1ba3cb96","tid":2277553,"uid":321228,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T14:23:19.000Z","msg":"比$500搵學生做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e8ce3dfa705f5e96f5b3481cf19efdeb71eb55","tid":2277553,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"窮鬼結婚拍咩戲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":